# Transformer Attention Accelerator 研究日誌

**Target**: Xilinx KV260 FPGA (117K LUT, 1248 DSP, 4GB DDR4)
**Benchmark**: TinyLlama-1.1B-Chat-v1.0 on HellaSwag full validation (10042 samples)
**Evaluation**: lm-evaluation-harness acc_norm (byte-length normalized)

---

## 目前架構

### 主機制: RAD-Cascade with PxV Mixed Precision

**Layer 0 (異質管線)**: 跑滿 64 dim, 8-bit 全精度 Q·K, 8-bit P·V

**Layer 1-21 (RAD-Cascade)**:

Stage 1 — Active + SIGN Compensation:
- Active dim: 24 (8-bit Q·K MAC)
  - 2 static Q-anchor pair (offline calibration, |Q|.mean top-2)
  - 1 static K-anchor pair (offline calibration K-max)
  - 9 dynamic pair (per-query top-9 by |Q| magnitude)
- Compensation dim: 40 (1-bit SIGN, β=0.5)
  - score += β × mean(|K_drop|) × Σ(|Q_drop| × sign(Q_drop) XNOR sign(K_drop))

Stage 2 — Block Adaptive Dispatch:
- Block size: 16 token
- Bypass: margin > signal_amp × 0.75 → 只送 top-1
- Overflow: 不滿足 → 送 score ≥ block_max - signal_amp × 0.25 的 token (≤ 3 per block)
- 候選 token 補算 40 dropped dim 滿血 8-bit

PxV Stage:
- P_THRES = 0.05
- attn_high (prob > 0.05): V 用 8-bit
- attn_low (prob ≤ 0.05): V 用 per-head 4-bit RTN 假量化
- 分配律: Out = attn_high @ V_8bit + attn_low @ V_4bit

