## 已驗證的跨架構性質

- BERT-Base MNLI 1000 sample v6: drop -0.10pp, MAC saving 49-56%
- TinyLlama HellaSwag 10042 RAD+PxV: drop 1.31pp, MAC saving 49.52%
- LLaMA outlier dim 位置跨 sample 穩定 ((A) cal vs (B) per-seq 完全一致)
- LLaMA outlier dim dominance 跨層不穩定 (Layer 5 top-15 dim 主導 91.5%, Layer 0/21 38-46%)

