## 硬體設計關鍵參數

- HEAD_DIM = 64
- NUM_PAIRS = 32 (每 pair 2 dim)
- STATIC_Q_PAIRS = 2, STATIC_K_PAIRS = 1, DYNAMIC_PAIRS = 9 (24-dim config)
- BLOCK_SIZE = 16
- MAX_LOCAL_TOKENS = 3 (per block stage 2 max)
- BETA = 0.5 (SIGN compensation 權重)
- P_THRES = 0.05 (PxV 分流門檻)
- 4-bit V 量化: per-head min/max RTN, 15 levels

異質管線: Layer 0 跑滿 64 dim (per-head average top-1/median = 4.23x, attention pattern 最分散)。
